      "content": "it just feels so heavy. like, i'm just performing this act of being alive every single day, but there's no one actually home anymore. if the story is over and the spark is gone, why is there such a massive pressure to just keep enduring the emptiness? it feels like i'm just prolonging the inevitable end of something that already died a long time ago.",
